<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #fff;
      color: #333;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    h1, h2 {
      color: #0076a3;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #ccc;
      padding-bottom: 4px;
    }
    .section {
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }
    .label {
      font-weight: bold;
      display: inline-block;
      width: 220px;
    }
    .signature {
      margin-top: 10px;
    }
    img.signature-img {
      border: 1px solid #ccc;
      max-width: 400px;
      height: auto;
      margin-top: 5px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <h1>üìã Pure Health & Wellness: New Appointment Submission</h1>

  <!-- Step 1 -->
  <div class="section">
    <h2>Step 1: Patient Info</h2>
    <p><span class="label">Name:</span><%= @data["firstName"] %> <%= @data["lastName"] %></p>
    <p><span class="label">Email:</span><%= @data["email"] %></p>
    <p><span class="label">Phone:</span><%= @data["phone"] %></p>
    <p><span class="label">Gender:</span><%= @data["gender"] %></p>
    <p><span class="label">Date of Birth:</span><%= "#{@data["dobMonth"]}/#{@data["dobDay"]}/#{@data["dobYear"]}" %></p>
    <p><span class="label">Driver‚Äôs License #:</span><%= @data["driversLicense"] %></p>
    <p><span class="label">Street Address:</span><%= @data["streetAddress"] %></p>
    <p><span class="label">City:</span><%= @data["city"] %></p>
    <p><span class="label">State:</span><%= @data["state"] %></p>
    <p><span class="label">Zip Code:</span><%= @data["zipCode"] %></p>
    <p><span class="label">Occupation:</span><%= @data["occupation"] %></p>
    <p><span class="label">Hours of Sleep:</span><%= @data["hoursOfSleep"] %></p>
    <p><span class="label">Health Goals:</span><%= @data["healthGoals"] %></p>
    <p><span class="label">Current Medications:</span><%= @data["currentMedications"] %></p>
    <p><span class="label">Marital Status:</span><%= @data["maritalStatus"] %></p>
    <p><span class="label">Has Children:</span><%= @data["hasChildren"] %></p>
    <% if @data["hasChildren"] == "yes" %>
      <p><span class="label">Number of Children:</span><%= @data["childrenCount"] %></p>
    <% end %>
  </div>

  <!-- Step 2 -->
  <div class="section">
    <h2>Step 2: Medical History</h2>
    <p><span class="label">Height:</span><%= @data["height"] %></p>
    <p><span class="label">Weight:</span><%= @data["weight"] %></p>
    <p><span class="label">Last Felt Well:</span><%= @data["lastFeltWell"] %></p>
    <p><span class="label">Tried Hormone Therapy Before:</span><%= @data["hormoneTherapyBefore"] %></p>
    <p><span class="label">Exercise Days/Week:</span><%= @data["exerciseDays"] %></p>
    <p><span class="label">Conditions:</span><%= @data["conditions"].join(", ") %></p>
    <p><span class="label">Family History:</span><%= @data["familyHistory"].join(", ") %></p>
    <p><span class="label">Social History:</span><%= @data["socialHistory"].join(", ") %></p>
    <p><span class="label">Allergies:</span><%= @data["allergies"] %></p>
    <p><span class="label">Motivation:</span><%= @data["motivation"] %></p>
    <p><span class="label">Symptoms:</span><%= @data["symptoms"].join(", ") %></p>
    <p><span class="label">Services Interested In:</span><%= @data["services"].join(", ") %></p>
  </div>

  <div style="page-break-before: always;"></div>

  <!-- Step 3 -->
  <div class="section">
    <h2>Step 3: Consent for Medical Services</h2>
    <p>This Consent for Medical Services (‚ÄúCONSENT‚Äù) specifies the terms and conditions under which, you, the undersigned patient (‚ÄúPATIENT‚Äù) may secure the availability of medical services offered by (‚ÄúPRACTICE‚Äù):</p>
    <p>Pure Health & Wellness 1130 Coffee Rd, Modesto, CA 95355</p>
    <p>This consent applies to the PRACTICE, its agents, employees and physician(s). PATIENT and the PRACTICE hereby enter into this agreement for provision of medical services specified herein (SERVICES). Wherefore, in exchange for consideration, the receipt and sufficiency of which the parties hereby acknowledge the PATIENT and PRACTICE agree as follows:</p>
    <p>The PATIENT acknowledges and agrees that this agreement has been entered into before the PRACTICE has provided the SERVICES specified herein to the PATIENT.</p>
    <p>The PATIENT acknowledges and agrees that this agreement has not been entered into at a time when the PATIENT is facing an emergency or an urgent health care situation.</p>
    <p>The PATIENT acknowledges reading and receiving a copy of the Notice of Privacy Practices, and by signing this agreement, the PATIENT authorizes the PRACTICE and its representatives to use and share PATIENT health information as described in the Notices of Privacy Practices.</p>
    <p>The PATIENT agrees to let PRACTICE, its agents, employees, and physician(s) provide medical care services. The SERVICES provided to the PATIENT may include:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Evaluation of patient medical history and lifestyle behaviors</li>
      <li>Physical examination</li>
      <li>Blood, urine, fecal, and/or saliva tests</li>
      <li>Diagnostic testing, bioelectrical and/or imaging tests</li>
      <li>Medical recommendations and management regarding my health issues and disease prevention</li>
      <li>Nutrition</li>
      <li>Nutritional supplementation and/or replacement</li>
      <li>Physical activity, functional performance, and exercise</li>
      <li>Lifestyle, environment, and behavior</li>
      <li>Stress response management</li>
      <li>Hormone replacement therapy</li>
      <li>Medication prescription management for those medications prescribed by the PRACTICE</li>
      <li>Procedures may include but are not limited to Injections, Intravenous infusion therapy, Aesthetic procedures</li>
    </ul>
    <p>PATIENT agrees that PRACTICE has not made any claims or statements about results or cures.</p>
    <p>Duration of Consent: PATIENT acknowledges the right to revoke this consent at any time except to the extent PRACTICE has already taken action in reliance on it. If PATIENT does not revoke it, this Consent will continue indefinitely. By signing this agreement, the PATIENT acknowledges that PATIENT has read and fully understands the information contained in this agreement. PATIENT agrees that everything in this Consent applies to current and future health care services provided by PRACTICE.</p>
  </div>



  <div class="section">
    <p><span class="label">Name:</span><%= @data["patientConsentForMedicalServicesPatientName"] %></p>
    <p><span class="label">DOB:</span><%= "#{@data["patientConsentForMedicalServicesDobMonth"]}/#{@data["patientConsentForMedicalServicesDobDay"]}/#{@data["patientConsentForMedicalServicesDobYear"]}" %></p>
    <p><span class="label">Date:</span><%= @data["patientConsentForMedicalServicesDate"] %></p>
    <div class="signature">
      <p><span class="label">Patient Signature:</span></p>
      <img class="signature-img" src="<%= @sig_patient_medical %>" alt="Patient Signature" />
    </div>
  </div>

  <div style="page-break-before: always;"></div>

  <!-- Step 4 -->
  <div class="section">
    <h2>Step 4: HGH Therapy Consent</h2>

    <p><span class="label">Patient Name:</span> <%= @data["informedConsentForHghReplacementTherapyPatientName"] %></p>
    <p><span class="label">Patient Date:</span> <%= @data["informedConsentForHghReplacementTherapyPatientDate"] %></p>
    <div class="signature">
      <p><span class="label">Patient Signature:</span></p>
      <img class="signature-img" src="<%= @sig_patient_hgh %>" alt="Patient Signature" />
    </div>

    <p><span class="label">Witness First Name:</span> <%= @data["informedConsentForHghReplacementTherapyWitnessFirstName"] %></p>
    <p><span class="label">Witness Last Name:</span> <%= @data["informedConsentForHghReplacementTherapyWitnessLastName"] %></p>
    <p><span class="label">Witness Date:</span> <%= @data["informedConsentForHghReplacementTherapyWitnessDate"] %></p>
    <div class="signature">
      <p><span class="label">Witness Signature:</span></p>
      <img class="signature-img" src="<%= @sig_witness_hgh %>" alt="Witness Signature" />
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <!-- Step 5 -->
  <div class="section">
    <h2>Step 5: Testosterone Therapy Consent</h2>
    <p><span class="label">Patient Name:</span><%= @data["informedConsentForTestosteroneReplacementTherapyPatientName"] %></p>
    <p><span class="label">Patient Date:</span><%= @data["informedConsentForTestosteroneReplacementTherapyPatientDate"] %></p>
    <div class="signature">
    <img class="signature-img" src="<%= @sig_patient_trt %>" alt="Patient Signature" />
    </div>
    <p><span class="label">Witness:</span><%= @data["informedConsentForTestosteroneReplacementTherapyWitnessFirstName"] %> <%= @data["informedConsentForTestosteroneReplacementTherapyWitnessLastName"] %></p>
    <p><span class="label">Witness Date:</span><%= @data["informedConsentForTestosteroneReplacementTherapyWitnessDate"] %></p>
    <div class="signature">
      <p><span class="label">Witness Signature:</span></p>
      <img class="signature-img" src="<%= @sig_witness_trt %>" alt="Witness Signature" />
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Step 6 -->
  <div class="section">
    <h2>Step 6: Controlled Substance Refill Consent</h2>
    <p><span class="label">Patient Name:</span><%= @data["controlledSubstanceAutoRefillConsentPatientName"] %></p>
    <p><span class="label">Date of Birth:</span><%= @data["controlledSubstanceAutoRefillConsentDob"] %></p>
    <div class="signature">
      <p><span class="label">Patient Signature:</span></p>
      <img class="signature-img" src="<%= @sig_patient_controlled %>" alt="Patient Signature" />
    </div>
  </div>

</body>
</html>